quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,"Annabi Lutu niriba daa labsi Naawuni tuumba  íirinima."
  26,161,"Saha shőĶli b…õ mabia Lutu ni daa yőĶliba: ‚ÄúDini b…ĒŇč…Ē yi ku zo Naawuni?‚ÄĚ"
  26,162,"‚ÄúAchiika! Mani ny…õla (Naawuni) tumo n-tin ya polo ni.‚ÄĚ"
  26,163,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,164,"‚ÄúYaha! M-bi b…Ēhiri ya sanyo‚Äô shőĶli, n-ka sanyoo m-pahila binnamda Duuma sani.‚ÄĚ"
  26,165,"‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yinim‚Äô niŇčdila dobba kobe binnamda puuni?‚ÄĚ"
  26,166,"‚ÄúKa yi chőĶri Naawuni ni nam sh…õli n-tin ya yi pa…£aba ni? Ch…õli gba! Yi ny…õla ninvu…£u shőĶba ban kpahi yőĶ…£i.‚ÄĚ"
  26,167,"Ka b…õ yőĶli: ‚ÄúYaa nyini Lutu! Achiika! A yi bi ch…õ (lala yőĶlt…Ē…£a), t…Ē! achiika! Ti ni yihi a y…õŇč…Ē.‚ÄĚ"
  26,168,"Ka o (Annabi Lutu) yőĶli: ‚ÄúAchiika! N-ny…õla Ňčun je yi tuma Ňč…Ē maa.‚ÄĚ"
  26,169,"(Ka oyőĶli): ‚ÄúYaa n Duuma (Naawuni)! Tilgim m mini m maligu ka ch…õ b…õ tuuntumsa Ňč…Ē maa.‚ÄĚ"
  26,170,"Ka Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) tilgi o mini o maligu zaasa namgbaniyini."
  26,171,"Na…£ila pa…£akpeen‚Äô so (Annabi Lutu pa…£a) n-daa ti pahi ban kpalim azaaba puuni."
  26,172,"Din nyaaŇča, ka Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) niŇč ninvu…£u sh…õba ban kpalim hallaka."
  26,173,"Ka Ti lahi mi sakurli (azaaba) m-pa b…õ zu…£u ka di shiri ny…õla mibu ni yőĶlimaŇčli, ka sa‚Äô sh…õli din mi ninvu…£u sh…õba b…õ ni daa sa…£isi maa daa niŇč din be."
  26,174,"Achiika! Ňä…Ē maa puuni mali kpahimbu. Amaa! B…õ (chőĶfurinim‚Äô) pam pala ban ti Naawuni yőĶlimaŇčli."
  26,175,"Yaha! Achiika! (Yaa nyini Annabi)! A Duuma (Naawuni) ny…õla NyőĶŇčda, Zaadali Namb…Ēoboznaa."
  26,176,"Aikati nima (Annabi Sayibu niriba) daa labsi Naawuni tuumba  íirinima."
  26,177,"Saha shőĶli Annabi Sayibu ni daa yőĶli ba: ‚ÄúDini b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi ku zo Naawuni?‚ÄĚ"
  26,178,"‚ÄúAchiika! Mani ny…õla tuun‚Äô so Ňčun ny…õ y…õmbahigalana n-tin ya.‚ÄĚ"
  26,179,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,180,"‚ÄúYaha! M-bi b…Ēhiri ya sanyo‚Äô shőĶli, n-ka sanyoo na…£ila binnamda Duuma sani.‚ÄĚ"
  26,181,"‚ÄúPalimi ya binzahindigu ka di pahi ya ban filindi za…£a (muuru) puuni.‚ÄĚ"
  26,182,"‚ÄúYaha! Zahimmi ya ni aadalsi binzahindigu.‚ÄĚ"
  26,183,"‚ÄúYaha! Di filindi ya niriba binyőĶra, ka di sa…£indi ya tiŇčgbani yaaŇča zu…£u.‚ÄĚ"